# Enterprise Performance & Accessibility Standards

## Performance Standards
* **Response Time** ≤ 200ms for 95th percentile
* **Throughput** ≥ 1000 requests/second
* **Error Rate** ≤ 0.1%
* **Availability** ≥ 99.9%
* **Performance Budgets** - Defined limits for key metrics

## Performance Optimization
* **Code splitting / lazy loading** for heavy UI or features
* **Static assets**: compress, cache, fingerprint; prefer modern formats
* **CDN Usage** - Global content delivery
* **Caching Strategy** - Multi-layer caching approach
* **Monitoring** - Real-time performance tracking

## Accessibility Standards
* **WCAG 2.2 AA** compliance baseline
* **Contrast ratios** meet minimum requirements
* **Keyboard navigation** fully functional
* **Screen reader** compatibility
* **Focus management** clear and logical
* **Color independence** - information not conveyed by color alone

## Accessibility Testing
* **Automated checks** in CI
* **Manual testing** with screen readers
* **Keyboard-only navigation** testing
* **Color contrast** validation
* **Alternative text** for all images

## Performance Monitoring
* **Core Web Vitals** tracking
* **Real User Monitoring (RUM)**
* **Synthetic monitoring** for critical paths
* **Performance budgets** enforcement
* **Continuous optimization** processes